304
00:31:09,600 --> 00:31:11,799
<i>Aku tak ingin dengar
tetek bengek itu.</i>

305
00:31:11,800 --> 00:31:12,999
<i>Aku mau kau datang ke sini,</i>

306
00:31:13,000 --> 00:31:15,399
