kami rekaman Elvis!

903
01:24:29,720 --> 01:24:31,319
Oh, Blue Hawaii.

904
01:24:31,320 --> 01:24:33,559
Kuharap kau tak keberatan.
Sedikit kebudayaan Amerika.

905
01:24:33,560 --> 01:24:34,719
Tidak sama sekali!

906
01:24:34,720 --> 01:24:37,079
Janet! /
Billy!

907
01:24:37,080 --> 01:24:39,799
Aku merindukanmu.

908
01:24:39,800 --> 01:24:43,719
Hei, semuanya,
aku rindu kalian.

909
01:24:43,720 --> 01:24:47,388
Jadi, apa di antara kalian
pernah diusik oleh pengganggu?

910
01:24:48,440 --> 01:24:49,679
Pete, di sekolah.

911
01:24:49,680 --> 01:24:52,079
Dia selalu mengejek Billy.

912
01:24:52,080 --> 01:24:55,119
