seberapa burukkah?

965
01:29:29,280 --> 01:29:31,519
Parah sekali.

966
01:29:31,520 --> 01:29:33,399
Semuanya masih tenang-tenang
saja di dalam sana?

967
01:29:33,400 --> 01:29:36,279
