Ya.

968
01:29:36,280 --> 01:29:38,359
Pasti ada sesuatu, bukan?

969
01:29:38,360 --> 01:29:41,279
Jika kita mampu membuktikan
tanpa keraguan sedikit pun...

970
01:29:41,280 --> 01:29:46,199
